com.example.n8tech.taskcan.Models

Class BidList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.n8tech.taskcan.Models.BidList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Bid>

    public class BidList
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<Bid>
    BidList contains an iterable ArrayList of Bid objects as well as methods that check for a specific bidder, return specific bidder indeces and the lowest bid on the list based on bid amount.
    See Also:
    Bid
